# Spec workflow: テンプレートと steering のみリポジトリで共有（それ以外はローカル）
.spec-workflow/*
!.spec-workflow/templates/
!.spec-workflow/templates/**
!.spec-workflow/steering/
!.spec-workflow/steering/**
.workspace-docs/
.serena/
docs/out
audit.log
./CLAUDE.md
./AGENTS.md

# MSBuild Binary and Structured Log
*.binlog

# MSTest test Results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*

